Finding best Decision  have to spend exponential amount of time
Actually NP hard Problem

We will find a tree which give a descent accuracy and exponentially ,uch easier to find(Greedy algoritm)

In our greedy algorithm we are not going to worry what will happen eventually and we will be greedy about each individual steps.

1.if Node is pure: output the only class
2.if no feature is left to split upon:output majority
